results.headline: CARO DIARIO (MOVIE)
results.summary_short: The director Nanni Moretti alternates wry encounters with soothing interludes in a film with three sections. At the start he is on his Vespa cruising Rome and reacting to films, locations and characters. Then he moves on to Stromboli and other islands in the company of a writer friend looking for a peaceful place to work. Finally, he examines his own medical crisis.
